{"tid":1702453,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"勇武可以擋子彈 和理非嘅請罷工","createTime":"2019-11-09T16:49:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T04:19:48.000Z","uid":137109,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5a243d33bdb5d17ddc8dcfe7bd63e02c34828f39","tid":1702453,"uid":137109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T16:49:43.000Z","msg":"除咗武力抗爭 有冇諗過<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">經濟</span></strong></span>先係政府/商家佬<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">最大春袋</span></span>?<br />\n罷工迫使政府讓步達成五大訴求 為義士追討公道 清算condom仔！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n先入咗所屬工會/成立公會 籌備一個目標為<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">長久癱瘓香港經濟嘅極大規模罷工行動</span></span></strong><br />\n(罷工成效事乎時間, 人數; 單日而細規模嘅話=山竹<br />\n要長久+大規模必要條件就係組織 公會並非大台 作用應以支援手足為主)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkonstrike\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSprZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=9ac0543d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkonstrike</a><br />\n<br />\n學生積極聯絡同系同學 成立關注組嚮應<br />\n(應屆dse學生建議罷課不罷學 大學唔可以冇咗你地)<br />\n<br />\n幫推+ 傳比身邊人<br />\n要打破同温層香港先有救<br />\n唔好吝嗇social media/任何途徑 住喺呢度 你有責任阻止香港沉淪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7322ead5173592ae583b16838decc4dc72e8e662","tid":1702453,"uid":137109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T16:49:55.000Z","msg":"推上熱門"},{"pid":"69fa365a66d8ffab8e349348e61621cbc55811da","tid":1702453,"uid":137109,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T16:50:39.000Z","msg":"罷佢老母<br />\n準備長期抗爭"},{"pid":"5a8d9d5d05eda20c3aad635493799f78672b6fd9","tid":1702453,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T16:52:11.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">而家只係叫你早D起身出門，唔好如常返返公司個位當無事發生過，咁都做唔到，香港人真係唔配有公義、民主同自由。。。。。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/re09Mt0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fre09Mt0.jpg&h=49aba454&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F9Pq4fG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF9Pq4fG.jpg&h=02c729ff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"052bb442714c7def0f33bfc9b0b920f2013d77d9","tid":1702453,"uid":137109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T16:53:21.000Z","msg":"得嗰小貓幾隻唔會成功<br />\n唔好因身邊冇人罷而退縮 用你嘅力量感染身邊人"},{"pid":"0a050b82747136f5485830d3332decef6447a010","tid":1702453,"uid":49016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T16:55:03.000Z","msg":"天下武功 唯快不破"},{"pid":"956e4729f49a006b07fa060a8240e735d7aad002","tid":1702453,"uid":137109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T16:55:23.000Z","msg":"最大春袋=經濟<br />\n香港之所以有國際地位因為外國擺錢落嚟<br />\n呢啲錢係我哋嘅最大籌碼"},{"pid":"3f508d47b42233c50cc07768ecb0f512e55c1c02","tid":1702453,"uid":137109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T16:55:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d3ca26597baa3ee45a35e8bf4f2612aba33296b","tid":1702453,"uid":137109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T16:57:17.000Z","msg":"推上去<br />\n唔要再見到放負po<br />\n罷工夠腳就係運動曙光"},{"pid":"23c2549199d7ed32b2e2fa23f252dda992b9239f","tid":1702453,"uid":137109,"like":0,"dis